All Implemented Interfaces:
EntityInitializer
public class ModelServerInitializer
extends ServerInitializer

ModelServerInitializer initializes an IDOL server that offers VRML models.

All of these implementations are similar:

  • CityServerInitializer
  • ModelServerInitializer
  • RasterServerInitializer
  • SatelliteServerInitializer
  • TrailServerInitializer

They differ in the description they give to the directory server and in the Queryable they use to perform spatiotemporal searches.

Consider refactoring these classes.
